, Rinko, Michelle)\nStep 2: 10,000 Coins + 1 Christmas Cake\nStep 3: 50,000 Coins + 2 Skill Tickets (Dubble)\nStep 4: 75,000 Coins + 1 Practice Ticket (Triple) + 2 Skill Tickets (Triple)\nStep 5: 100,000 Coins + 10 Miracle Crystals + 1 Skill Ticket (Premium)\n\nFeaturing ★★ and higher members! \nOne ★★★ member guaranteed!\nNew ★★★ and higher members come with a new costume!",null,null,null],"term":[null,"2019/12/02 08:00 ～ 2019/12/07 07:59 UTC",null,null,null],"newMemberInfo":[null,null,null,null,null],"notice":[null,"・All members drop with their pre-Training images.\n・Duplicate members may drop when playing the gacha.\n・Duplicate members will automatically be sent to the Waiting Room.\n・Each individual drop is performed according to the gacha drop rates. Example: 100 plays will not necessarily result in 1 drop of a member that has a 1% drop rate.\n・Members from the Nostalgic Snow Globe Gacha will be featured in this gacha as well. However, drop rates will vary.\n・For more on featured members and drop rates, check Gacha Details.\n・Limited Edition Members will be unavailable after this gacha ends. However, they may also be featured in future gacha. Details regarding this are TBD.\n・For more on parameters and skills of Limited Edition Members, check Member Details. \n・Even in the event that the Gacha Results screen did not display because the app was forced to close or connection was interrupted, members will be obtained. Please check the Member List or the Waiting Room.\n・Campaign schedule may be subject to change without prior notice. ",null,null,null]}}